com.radiantlogic.iddm.base

Interface AuthenticationResponse

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Response
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LdapResponse

    public interface AuthenticationResponse
extends Response
    Marker interface for AuthenticationOperations responses that potentially can be returned to IDDM for processing.

    Implementing this interface alone does not make a response valid or guarantee it will be accepted by IDDM.

    It is strongly recommended (but not required) that developers use a provided concrete implementation, such as LdapResponse, instead of directly implementing this interface.
